msgstr "是 Wine 文件管理器，其设计与早期的 Microsoft Windows 资源管理器类似。"

#: sw_data.py:2449
msgid ""
"is a GUI uninstaller for all setup programs that put an uninstall entry in "
"the registry. It's similar in function to 'Add/Remove Programs' in Windows, "
"except much simpler."
msgstr ""
"是适用于所有安装程序的 GUI 卸载程序，它会在注册表中放置一个卸载条目。它的功能"
"类似于 Windows 中的“添加/删除程序”，但要简单得多。"

#: sw_data.py:2454
msgid ""
"is a helper script to download and install various redistributable runtime "
"libraries needed to run some programs in Wine."
msgstr ""
"是一个辅助脚本，用于下载和安装在 Wine 中运行某些程序所需的各种可再发行的运行"
"时库。"

